* Granularity\nDecision Factors
** Business Requirements
***_ Most detailed analysis required
***_ Anomaly detection → millisecond
***_ Daily reports → hourly aggregate
** Query Patterns
***_ Frequent aggregation → coarser grain
***_ Drill-down needed → finer grain
** Storage & Compute Costs
***_ Finer = more rows = higher cost
***_ Coarser = fewer rows = lower cost
** Compliance/Audit
***_ Regulatory mandates may require fine grain
***_ Document compliance requirements
@endmindmap
